<p>ьЩ╝ьк╜ ъ╖╕ыЮШэФДьЧРьДЬ 9ы▓И эЩХыеаьЭ┤ 1.0ьЭ┤ьзАызМ ьШдые╕ьк╜ ъ╖╕ыЮШэФДьЧРьДЬыКФ 0.4xыбЬ ьдДъ│а ыВШыи╕ьзА ы▓ИэШ╕ыУдьЭШ ьаХы│┤ыУдьЭ┤ ыУЬыЯмыВШыКФ ъ▓ГьЭД ы│╝ ьИШ ьЮИьК╡ыЛИыЛд. ьжЙ, softmaxыбЬ ьаХы│┤ъ░А ьВмыЭ╝ьзАыКФ ым╕ьаЬые╝ ьКдь╝АьЭ╝ызБьЬ╝ыбЬ эХ┤ъ▓░эХа ьИШ ьЮИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>ыШРэХЬ, $d_k$ые╝ ьВмьЪйэХШыКФ ьЭ┤ьЬаыКФ ыЛдьЭМъ│╝ ъ░ЩьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>QueryьЩА Keyъ░А ъ░АьЪ░ьЛЬьХИ ы╢ДэПмые╝ ыФ░ые╕ыЛдъ│а ъ░АьаХэХШый┤ эПЙъ╖аьЭА 0, ы╢ДьВ░ьЭА 1ьЭД ъ░АьзАъ▓М ыРйыЛИыЛд. $QK^{\top} = \sum_{i}^{d_k}Q_iK_i$ьЭ┤ъ│а QueryьЩА KeyыКФ independentэХШыпАыбЬ эПЙъ╖аьЭА 0, ы╢ДьВ░ьЭА $d_k$ые╝ ъ░АьзАъ▓М ыРйыЛИыЛд. ыФ░ыЭ╝ьДЬ $\sqrt{d_k}$ыбЬ ьКдь╝АьЭ╝ызБэХШьЧм ы╢ДьВ░ьЭД 1ыбЬ ьдДьЭ╝ ьИШ ьЮИъ▓М ыРйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">scaled_dot_product_attention</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">query</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">value</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">attn_mask</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">bool_</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">None</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">:</span>
  <span class="s">"""
  Query (B, seq_len_q, d_k)
  Key (B, seq_len_k, d_k)
  Value (B, seq_len_k, d_v)
  """</span>
  <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">scaled_factor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">math</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">query</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
  <span class="n">attn_weight</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">query</span> <span class="o">@</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">swapaxes</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">scaled_factor</span> <span class="c1"># (B, seq_len_q, seq_len_k)
</span>  <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">attn_mask</span> <span class="ow">is</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="bp">None</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">attn_weight</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">masked_fill</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">attn_weight</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">attn_mask</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">float</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'-inf'</span><span class="p">))</span>
  <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">attn_weight</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">softmax</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">attn_weight</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">attn_weight</span> <span class="o">@</span> <span class="n">value</span> <span class="c1"># (B, seq_len_q, d_v)
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>attention padding mask ь▓ШыЯ╝ ьЦ┤эЕРьЕШ ьКдь╜ФьЦ┤ьЧР ызИьКдэВ╣ьЭД ьЬДэХЬ masked_fill эХиьИШыКФ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">numpy.ma.array</code>ые╝ ьЭ┤ьЪйэХШьЧм ъ╡мэШДэЦИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<h2 id="backward">Backward</h2>
<p>Backward эХиьИШые╝ ъ╡мэШДэХШъ╕░ ьЬДэХ┤ Attention ъ│ДьВ░ьЧР ь░╕ьЧмэХШыКФ Query, Key, Value ьД╕ ъ░АьзА ьЮЕыаеьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ъ░А эХДьЪФэХйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>ыи╝ьаА, Attention forward ьИШьЛЭьЭД ыВШыИаьДЬ ьГЭъ░БэХ┤ы│┤ъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$1. \ A = \frac{QK^{\top}}{\sqrt{d_k}}$<br />
$2. \ W = \text{softmax}(A)$<br />
$3. \ Z = WV$</p>

<p>1ы▓И ьИШьЛЭьЬ╝ыбЬы╢АэД░ $\frac{\partial A}{\partial Q}$ьЩА $\frac{\partial A}{\partial K}$ые╝ ъ╡мэХа ьИШ ьЮИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial A}{\partial Q} = \frac{K}{\sqrt{d_k}}$</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial A}{\partial K} = \frac{Q}{\sqrt{d_k}}$</p>

<p>2ы▓И ьИШьЛЭьЧРьДЬ ьЦ╗ьЭД ьИШ ьЮИыКФ $\frac{\partial W}{\partial A}$ыКФ softmaxьЭШ ып╕ы╢Дъ▓░ъ│╝ьЭ┤ыпАыбЬ W(1 - W)ыбЬ ъ░АьаХэХ┤ы│┤ъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд.(ьЛдьаЬ ъ│ДьВ░ьЭА W(1 - W)ъ░А ьХДыЛЩыЛИыЛд. ьаАыКФ ып╕ыжм ъ╡мэШДэХ┤ыСФ softmax эБ┤ыЮШьКдые╝ ьЭ┤ьЪйэХа ъ▓ГьЮЕыЛИыЛд.)</p>

<p>ыШРэХЬ, 3ы▓И ьИШьЛЭьЬ╝ыбЬы╢АэД░ $\frac{\partial Z}{\partial W} = V^{\top}$ыПД ьХМ ьИШ ьЮИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>ыЛдьЭМ, ValueьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ы╢АэД░ ъ│ДьВ░эХйыЛИыЛд. upstream gradientые╝ $dZ$ыЭ╝ ъ░АьаХэХШъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial V} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial Z} \frac{\partial Z}{\partial V} = W^{\top} dZ$</p>

<p>ыЛдьЭМ, QueryьЩА KeyьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ъ│ДьВ░эХйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial Q} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial Z} \frac{\partial Z}{\partial W} \frac{\partial W}{\partial A} \frac{\partial A}{\partial Q} = dZ \cdot W(1-W) \cdot \frac{K}{\sqrt{d_k}}$</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial K} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial Z} \frac{\partial Z}{\partial W} \frac{\partial W}{\partial A} \frac{\partial A}{\partial K} = dZ \cdot W(1-W) \cdot \frac{Q}{\sqrt{d_k}}$</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">scaled_dot_product_attention_backward</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">dz</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">Tuple</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">]:</span>
  <span class="s">"""
  dz (B, seq_len_q, d_v)
  self.attn_weight (B, seq_len_q, seq_len_k)
  self.q (B, seq_len_q, d_k)
  self.k (B, seq_len_k, d_k)
  self.v (B, seq_len_k, d_v)
  """</span>
