</code></pre></div></div>

<h1 id="layernorm">LayerNorm</h1>
<p>NormalizationьЭА ьЮЕыаеъ░ТьЧР ыМАэХ┤ ьаХъ╖ЬэЩФэХШъ╕░ ьЬДэХЬ ъ│╝ьаХьЮЕыЛИыЛд. эХЩьК╡ ыН░ьЭ┤эД░ые╝ ы░░ь╣Ш ыЛиьЬДыбЬ эХЩьК╡эХа ыХМ, ыЮЬыНдэХШъ▓М ьГШэФМызБыРЬ ы░░ь╣ШыУдьЭШ ыН░ьЭ┤эД░ ы╢ДэПмъ░А ыЛдые╝ ьИШ ьЮИьК╡ыЛИыЛд. ьЭ┤ыЯмэХЬ ы░░ь╣Шые╝ ъ╖╕ыМАыбЬ эХЩьК╡эХШъ▓М ыРШый┤ ъ╖╕ьЧР ызЮъ▓М ыДдэК╕ьЫМэБмыКФ ъ░АьдСь╣Шые╝ ьб░ьаИэХШъ▓М ыРШыКФыН░ ьЭ┤ыбЬ ьЭ╕эХ┤ эХЩьК╡ьЧР ыУдьЭ┤ыКФ ьЛЬъ░ДьЭ┤ ьжЭъ░АыРа ьИШ ьЮИьК╡ыЛИыЛд. ыФ░ыЭ╝ьДЬ, ьаХъ╖ЬэЩФые╝ эЖ╡эХ┤ ыН░ьЭ┤эД░ ы╢ДэПмые╝ ьб░ьаХэХШьЧм ьХИьаХьаБьЭ┤ъ│а эХЩьК╡ьЭ┤ ы╣аые┤ъ▓М ьЭ┤ыгиьЦ┤ьзАыПДыбЭ эХШыКФ ъ╕░ы▓ХьЭ┤ NormalizationьЮЕыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>ы░░ь╣Ш ыЛиьЬДыбЬ ьаХъ╖ЬэЩФые╝ ьзДэЦЙэХШыКФ Batch Normalization(BN), ыН░ьЭ┤эД░ feature ыЛиьЬДыбЬ ьаХъ╖ЬэЩФые╝ ьзДэЦЙэХШыКФ Layer Normalization(LN), BatchNormъ│╝ LayerNormьЭШ эК╣ьзХьЭД ьДЮьЭА Group Normalization(GN)ьЭ┤ ьЮИьК╡ыЛИыЛд. ьЧмъ╕░ьДЬыКФ Layer NormalizationьЭД ъ╡мэШДэХйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>Layer NormalizationьЭА ъ░Б ьГШэФМызИыЛд ыкиыУа featureыУдьЧР ыМАэХ┤ эПЙъ╖аьЭД 0, ы╢ДьВ░ьЭД 1ыбЬ ьб░ьаХэХШьЧм ы░░ь╣Ш ьВмьЭ┤ьжИьЧР ьЭШьб┤ьаБьЭ┤ьзА ьХКъ▓М ыРйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>ыШРэХЬ, RNN ъ│ДьЧ┤ьЭШ ыкиыН╕ьЭА BNьЭД ьВмьЪйэХШъ╕░ ьЦ┤ыа╡ьК╡ыЛИыЛд. ьЩЬыГРэХШый┤, SequentialэХЬ ыкиыН╕ьЭА ъ░Б эГАьЮДьКдэЕЭьЧР ыФ░ыЭ╝ ыЛдые╕ ыН░ьЭ┤эД░ъ░А ыУдьЦ┤ьЩАьХ╝ эХШъ│а ъ╕╕ьЭ┤ъ░А ыЛдые╕ ъ▓╜ьЪ░ padding ь▓Шыжмъ░А эХДьЪФэЦИьК╡ыЛИыЛд. ъ╖╕ыЮШьДЬ ы░░ь╣Ш ьаХъ╖ЬэЩФые╝ ьаБьЪйэХШъ╕░ ьЦ┤ыадьЫаъ╕░ ыХМым╕ьЧР LNьЭД ьаБьЪйэХйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<h2 id="forward-2">Forward</h2>
<p>LNьЭШ ьИШьЛЭьЭА ыЛдьЭМъ│╝ ъ░ЩьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$y = \frac{x - E[x]}{\sqrt{Var[x] + \epsilon}} * \gamma + \beta$</p>

<p>$\gamma$ьЩА $\beta$ыКФ эХЩьК╡ъ░АыКеэХЬ эММыЭ╝ып╕эД░ьЮЕыЛИыЛд. $\gamma$ьЩА $\beta$ые╝ ьВмьЪйэХШыКФ ьЭ┤ьЬаыКФ NormalizationьЬ╝ыбЬ ьЭ╕эХ┤ ыН░ьЭ┤эД░ эК╣ьД▒ьЭ┤ ьВмыЭ╝ьзАыКФыН░ ьЭ┤ъ▓ГьЭ┤ эХЩьК╡эХШыКФыН░ ъ╖╕ыжм ьвЛьзА ык╗эХйыЛИыЛд. ъ╖╕ыЮШьДЬ эММыЭ╝ып╕эД░ые╝ ь╢Фъ░АэХШьЧм ыДдэК╕ьЫМэБмъ░А эХЩьК╡эХШъ╕░ ьвЛыПДыбЭ ьКдь╝АьЭ╝ызБ, ьЛЬэФДэК╕ ьЮСьЧЕьЭД ьИШэЦЙэХШъ╕░ ьЬДэХ┤ $\gamma$
ьЩА $\beta$ъ░А ь╢Фъ░АыРШьЧИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">forward</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">input</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">input</span>
    <span class="n">dims</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">tuple</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">normalized_shape</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="c1"># dim=3 -&gt; (2,1,0)
</span>    <span class="n">normalized</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">input</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">dims</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">var</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dims</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">eps</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">elementwise_affine</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">normalized</span> <span class="o">*=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">weight</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">bias</span> <span class="ow">is</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="bp">None</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">normalized</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">bias</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">normalized</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="backward-2">Backward</h2>
<p>ыи╝ьаА, ьИШьЛЭьЭД ыЛдьЭМъ│╝ ъ░ЩьЭ┤ ы╢ДыжмэХШьЧм ьГЭъ░БэХ┤ы│┤ъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>$\mu = \frac{1}{N}\sum x$</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>$\sigma^2 = \frac{1}{N}\sum(x - \mu)^2$</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>$\hat{x} = \frac{x-\mu}{\sqrt{\sigma^2 + \epsilon}}$</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>$y = \gamma \hat{x} + \beta$</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>ыи╝ьаА, $\hat{x}$ьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ъ│ДьВ░эХШъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \hat{x}} = \gamma$</p>

<p>ыЛдьЭМ, ы╢ДьВ░ьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ъ│ДьВ░эХШъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \sigma^2} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial \hat{x}} \cdot \frac{\partial \hat{x}}{\partial \sigma^2}$</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial \hat{x}}{\partial \sigma^2} = -\frac{1}{2}(x - \mu)(\sigma^2 + \epsilon)^{-\frac{3}{2}}$</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \sigma^2} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial \hat{x}} \cdot -\frac{1}{2}(x - \mu)(\sigma^2 + \epsilon)^{-\frac{3}{2}}$</p>

<p>ыЛдьЭМ, эПЙъ╖аьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ъ│ДьВ░эХШъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд. 2ы▓ИьЧРьДЬ ы╢ДьВ░ьЭД ъ│ДьВ░эХа ыХМ эПЙъ╖аьЭ┤ ь░╕ьЧмэХШыпАыбЬ ы╢ДьВ░ьЭД эПЙъ╖аьЬ╝ыбЬ ып╕ы╢ДэХШьЧм ьЦ╗ьЭА ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ыПД ь╢Фъ░АыРШьЦ┤ьХ╝ эХйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \mu} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial \hat{x}} \cdot \frac{\partial \hat{x}}{\partial \mu} + \frac{\partial L}{\partial \sigma^2} \cdot \frac{\partial \sigma^2}{\partial \mu}$</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial \sigma^2}{\partial \mu} = -\frac{2}{N}(x - \mu)$</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial \mu} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial \hat{x}} \cdot -\frac{1}{\sqrt{\sigma^2 + \epsilon}} + \frac{\partial L}{\partial \sigma^2} \cdot -\frac{2}{N}(x-\mu)$</p>

<p>ызИьзАызЙьЬ╝ыбЬ, xьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ъ│ДьВ░эХШъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial x} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial \hat{x}} \cdot \frac{\partial \hat{x}}{\partial x} + \frac{\partial L}{\partial \mu} \cdot \frac{\partial \mu}{\partial x} + \frac{\partial L}{\partial \sigma^2} \cdot \frac{\partial \sigma^2}{\partial x}$</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial L}{\partial x} = \frac{\partial L}{\partial \hat{x}} \cdot \frac{1}{\sqrt{\sigma^2 + \epsilon}} + \frac{\partial L}{\partial \sigma^2} \cdot \frac{2}{N}(x - \mu) + \frac{\partial L}{\partial \mu} \cdot \frac{1}{N}$</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">backward</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">dz</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">Tuple</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">]:</span>
    <span class="n">E</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">dz</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x_flat</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">E</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">mean</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x_flat</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">variance</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">var</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x_flat</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">std</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">variance</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">eps</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">x_hat</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x_flat</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">std</span>

    <span class="n">grad_xhat</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">dz</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">weight</span>
    <span class="n">grad_xhat_flat</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">grad_xhat</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">E</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">grad_var</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">grad_xhat_flat</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x_flat</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">0.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">std</span> <span class="o">**</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">grad_mean</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">grad_xhat_flat</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">std</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">grad_var</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x_flat</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">dx_flat</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">grad_xhat_flat</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">std</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">grad_var</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x_flat</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">E</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">grad_mean</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">E</span>
    <span class="n">dx</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">dx_flat</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">dw</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dz</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">x_hat</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">))</span>
    <span class="n">db</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dz</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">))</span>

    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">dx</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">dw</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">db</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>ь╜ФыУЬыбЬ ъ╡мэШДэХа ыХМыКФ epsilon ъ░ТьЭД 0ьЬ╝ыбЬ ъ░АьаХэХШьЧм ъ╡мэШДыРШьЧИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<h1 id="gelu">GELU</h1>
<p>GELUыКФ ReLUьЭШ ыЛиьаРьЭД ы│┤ьЩДэХЬ эЩЬьД▒эЩФ эХиьИШьЮЕыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>ReLUыКФ ыЛдьЭМьЭШ ъ╖╕ыЮШэФДьЩА ъ░ЩьЭ┤ ьЮЕыаеъ░ТьЭ┤ ьЭМьИШьЭ╝ ъ▓╜ьЪ░ 0ьЭД ь╢ЬыаеэХШьЧм ыЙ┤ыЯ░ьЭ┤ ьг╜ыКФ эШДьГБьЭ╕ Dying ReLU ым╕ьаЬъ░А ы░ЬьГЭэЦИьК╡ыЛИыЛд. ьЮЕыаеыРЬ ъ░ТьЭ┤ ьЭМьИШъ░А эХЬы▓ИьЭ┤ыЭ╝ыПД ыУ▒ьЮеэХШъ▓М ыРШый┤ эЩЬьД▒эЩФ эХиьИШьЭШ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ъ░А 0ьЭ┤ыпАыбЬ ъ╖╕ ыЙ┤ыЯ░ъ│╝ ьЧ░ъ▓░ыРЬ ыЛдые╕ ыЙ┤ыЯ░ыУд ыШРэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ъ░А 0ьЭ┤ ыРйыЛИыЛд. ыМАьХИьЬ╝ыбЬ ьЭМьИШ ьЮЕыаеьЧРыПД ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ьаЬъ│╡эХШыКФ leaky reluъ░А ьЮИьзАызМ ьЭМьИШьЧР ыМАэХЬ boundaryъ░А ьЧЖъ╕░ ыХМым╕ьЧР ьЦ┤ыЦаэХЬ ьЭМьИШъ░ТьЧР ыМАэХ┤ьДЬыПД ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ьаЬъ│╡эХ┤ы▓Дыж╜ыЛИыЛд. ъ╖╕ыЮШьДЬ swishыВШ GELUьЩА ъ░ЩьЭ┤ ьЭМьИШ boundaryые╝ ьаЬъ│╡эХШыКФ эЩЬьД▒эЩФ эХиьИШъ░А ьаЬьХИыРШьЧИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

