</figure>

<p>эХШьзАызМ, NLP эГЬьКдэБмьЧРьДЬ ъ╝н GELUьЧмьХ╝ эХШыКФ ьЭ┤ьЬаыКФ ьЮШ ыкиые┤ъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд. ыЛдые╕ ы╕ФыбЬъ╖╕ьЧРьДЬыКФ тАЬReLUыВШ ELUы│┤ыЛд GELUъ░А ьД▒ыКеьЭ┤ ьвЛьХШыЛдтАЭьаХыПДыбЬызМ ыЛдыУд ъ╕░ыбЭэХШъ│а ьЮИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.<br />
ъ░АьЪ░ьЛЬьХИ ы╢ДэПмьЭШ ьЧ░ьЖНьД▒ьЭ┤ ьЮДы▓аыФйьЩА ъ░ЩьЭА ы▓бэД░ эХЩьК╡ьЧР ьЬаыжмэХШъ╕░ ыХМым╕ьЭ╝ ьИШыПД ьЮИьзАызМ ьаХэЩХэХЬ ьЭ┤ьЬаые╝ ь░╛ъ╕░ ьЦ┤ыадьЫаьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<h2 id="forward-3">Forward</h2>
<p>GELUыКФ ъ░АьЪ░ьЛЬьХИ ы╢ДэПмьЭШ ыИДьаБ ы╢ДэПм эХиьИШ(CDF)ьЩА ьЮЕыаеъ░ТьЭД ъ│▒эХШыКФ эЩЬьД▒эЩФ эХиьИШьЮЕыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\text{GELU}(x) = x \cdot \Phi(x)$</p>

<p>ьаЬъ░А ъ╡мэШДэХа ыХМыКФ tanhыбЬ ъ╖╝ьВмэХЬ ьИШьЛЭьЭД ьВмьЪйэЦИьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\text{GELU}(x) = 0.5 * x * (1 + \text{tanh}(\sqrt{2/\pi} * (x + 0.044715 * x^3)))$</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">forward</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">:</span>
  <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">x</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mf">0.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">tanh</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">pi</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">0.044715</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="backward-3">Backward</h2>
<p>ып╕ы╢ДьЭД эХШъ╕░ ьЬДэХ┤ ьИШьЛЭьЭД ыСРъ░ЬыбЬ ыВШыИДьЦ┤ ьГЭъ░БэХ┤ы│┤ъ▓аьК╡ыЛИыЛд.</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>$\text{GELU}(x) = 0.5x(1 + \text{tanh}(y))$</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>$y = \sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}(x + 0.044715x^3)$</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>ыи╝ьаА, 1ы▓И ьИШьЛЭьЧРьДЬ $\hat{x}$ьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ъ│ДьВ░эХйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial \text{GELU}}{\partial x} = 0.5(1 + \text{tanh}(y)) + 0.5x\frac{\partial \text{tanh}(y)}{\partial x}$</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial \text{tanh}(y)}{\partial x} = (1 - \text{tanh}^2(y))\frac{\partial y}{\partial x}$</p>

<p>ыЛдьЭМ, 2ы▓И ьИШьЛЭьЧРьДЬ xьЧР ыМАэХЬ ъ╕░ьЪ╕ъ╕░ые╝ ъ│ДьВ░эХйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial y}{\partial x} = \sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}(1 + 0.044715 * 3 * x^2)$</p>

<p>ызИьзАызЙьЬ╝ыбЬ, ьаХыжмэХйыЛИыЛд.</p>

<p>$\frac{\partial \text{GELU}}{\partial x} = 0.5(1 + \text{tanh}(y)) + 0.5x(1 - \text{tanh}^2(y))\sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}(1 + 0.044715 * 3 * x^2)$</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">backward</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">dz</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">-&gt;</span> <span class="n">NDArray</span><span class="p">:</span>
  <span class="n">tanh_y</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">tanh</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">pi</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">0.044715</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">))</span>
  <span class="n">dy_dx</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">pi</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">3</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mf">0.044715</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="n">dx</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">tanh_y</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">0.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">tanh_y</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">dy_dx</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">dz</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">dx</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

